User - Class in edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.model.entity
User entity in the database to store information in regards to various users such as: User ID, OAuthKey, their name, a biography section, and an image path for the user pictures.
User() - Constructor for class edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.model.entity.User
 
UserController - Class in edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.controller
REST Controller class for User to receive parameter values taken from HTTP requests to their respective specified URL endpoints, and returning serialized JSON object results to HTTP responses.

UserRepository - Interface in edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.model.dao
The UserRepository extends the JpaRepository, which provides the CRUD (create, read, update, delete) functions, as well as providing the ability to delete records in batches.
UserService - Class in edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.service
User service class to be used and injected in the UserController.
